channel.title: Looking for a source with little editing
channel.description:
Hi there, I've been looking for a source lately that doesn't really have much editing done to it(fast exp, custom shops, portals, etc), but I can't seem to find one. If someone could point me in the right direction that would be great.
If possible it would be nice if the source already had skills/items(like godswords)/special bar working.
